    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝森特表示，华尔街巨头正在寻找特朗普获胜的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/wall-street-titans-looking-for-signs-trump-can-win-bessent-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Key Square Group LP 创始人 Scott Bessent 表示，华尔街投资者在权衡投资决策时，正在寻找唐纳德·特朗普可能在 11 月击败总统乔·拜登的指标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/wall-street-titans-looking-for-signs-trump-can-win-bessent-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 22:13:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陷入困境的石油公司 Petroperu 董事会敦促政府私有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/board-of-ailing-oil-firm-petroperu-pushes-government-to-privatize</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于亏损持续增加，陷入困境的国有石油公司秘鲁国家石油公司董事会正在敦促政府将该公司的多数股权出售给私营部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/board-of-ailing-oil-firm-petroperu-pushes-government-to-privatize</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 22:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党拉米在基辅访问期间誓言“铁定”支持乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/labour-s-lammy-vows-ironclad-support-for-ukraine-on-kyiv-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党的大卫·拉米和约翰·希利在影子内阁的两名高级成员访问基辅时承诺，如果反对党赢得即将到来的大选，英国将维持英国支持乌克兰对抗俄罗斯的“铁定”承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/labour-s-lammy-vows-ironclad-support-for-ukraine-on-kyiv-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国废食用油泛滥引发美国提高关税的呼声</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/flood-of-chinese-used-cooking-oil-spurs-call-to-boost-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统乔·拜登准备对中国征收新一波关税之际，美国一个大豆贸易组织正在推动对中国废食用油征收更高的关税，该组织称这会削弱美国用于生物燃料的农作物的产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/flood-of-chinese-used-cooking-oil-spurs-call-to-boost-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 21:26:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迈克尔·科恩的证词将特朗普与支付封口费联系在一起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/michael-cohen-testimony-ties-trump-to-hush-money-payment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈克尔·科恩 (Michael Cohen) 直接将唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 与向成人电影女演员斯托米·丹尼尔斯 (Stormy Daniels) 支付封口费联系起来，以便在 2016 年大选前不让他们所谓的性接触成为新闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/michael-cohen-testimony-ties-trump-to-hush-money-payment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 21:06:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
